&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Market Data Developer&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Cumberland team. This role is responsible for building and supporting a C++ based technology stack that empowers Cumberland to trade across many exchanges and regions using a wide range of strategies.&lt;/p&gt;
